  "title": "Sales and Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p>Reporting to Sales Director,  this role is responsible for developing and maintaining customer relationships, driving sales and meeting sales and profit targets.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· Build and maintain existing customer relationships &amp; achieve sales targets</p>\n<p>· Identify new sales opportunities for company’s products and services</p>\n<p>· Develop and manage sales budget, forecasts and establish pricing strategies</p>\n<p>· Coordinate production with factory &amp; ensure product availability</p>\n<p>· Working with Warehouse to ensure timely delivery</p>\n<p>· Provide after-sales support such as following up on customers’ feedback, managing after-sales issues</p>\n<p>· Attend or participate in exhibitions &amp; trade shows to promote companies products and services</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Bachelor degree or Diploma in Business &amp; Marketing or Civil, Mechanical or Material Science</p>\n<p>· At least 2 years of sales and marketing experience, preferably in building / construction sector</p>\n<p>· Self-motivated, independent and resourceful</p>\n<p>· Effective team player with good communication and negotiation skills</p>\n<p>· Proficient in Microsoft Office applications</p>\n<p>· Willing to travel frequently for customer visits and business meetings</p>",
